results.cleanName: Speed Duel GX Duel Academy Box

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value:
Designed to allow 8 players to jump straight into their own tournament
• Contains "Elemental HERO" cards used by Jaden Yuki, as well as cards used by Aster Phoenix and Dr. Vellian Crowler, among others.
• Introduces many new cards to Speed Duels.
• Includes Secret Rare variants of popular GX-era cards.
